Monopoly.Tiles

Class PropertyTile

  • java.lang.Object
    • Monopoly.Tiles.Tile
      • Monopoly.Tiles.OwnableTile
        • Monopoly.Tiles.PropertyTile

  • public class PropertyTile
extends OwnableTile
    The PropertyTile is an subclass of Tile. It contains fields associated more specifically with those of colored properties on a Monopoly game board.
